config USR_LIB_ISO7816
  bool  "iso7816-3 protocol stack (without platform dependencies)"
  default y
  select USR_DRV_DRVISO7816
  ---help---
  Support for the iso7816-3 standard, excluding the platform
  specific interface, hosted in the dedicated iso7816 driver.
  For the iso7816 standard T=0 & T=1 are supported.

